{"id":666861,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/666861.html","date":"2021-06-05T14:35:32Z","modified":"2021-06-05T14:36:10Z","title":"匿名网友 | 在线众包多媒体项目《广场犹在》","content":"<p>有匿名网友在线上协作工具 Padlet 上建立了<a href=\"https://padlet.com/cyl1543658970/dofoiedk1x59f09f\" title=\"“广场犹在”\">“广场犹在”</a>的项目，搜集了与六四天安门事件有关的歌曲、摄影、诗歌、新闻、纪录片、文章、信件、广播节目等不同媒介，同时也接受匿名投稿，在线上建立起了一座“六四纪念馆”。</p>\n<p>项目地址是：<a href=\"https://padlet.com/cyl1543658970/dofoiedk1x59f09f\">https://padlet.com/cyl1543658970/dofoiedk1x59f09f</a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_666862\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-666862\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/06/64.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"auto\" class=\"size-full wp-image-666862\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/06/64.jpg 1788w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/06/64-300x184.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/06/64-1024x629.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/06/64-768x472.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/06/64-1536x944.jpg 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/06/64-1080x664.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1788px) 100vw, 1788px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-666862\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">“广场犹在”项目截图</p></div>\n","author":1079,"categories":[43134,41492,38912,18271],"tags":[22306]}